k through your dance moves.\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I understand, OK, so is there anything else you'd like to tell us?\\\"\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fallon wondered.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The comedian continued spoofing Gunn's most famous moves - including hopping from side to side with her arms out to resemble a kangaroo as an ode to her country.\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1432, \"end\": 1436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9310119275412008, \"rank\": 0.07384650188739066, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fallon also got in on the action and started kangaroo hopping with Dratch before getting on the floor and imitating the windmill move.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dratch eventually kangaroo hopped off the stage while Fallon thanked her for the appearance.\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The audience roared with applause and laughter.\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1839, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn found herself in the spotlight after she received zero points for her breaking competition last Friday.\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1841, \"end\": 1845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9310119275412008, \"rank\": 0.07384650188739066, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The dancer - who also works as a professor in Sydney - latertold ESPNthat she knew she was \\\"never going to beat these girls on what they do best,\\\" which is their \\\"power\\\" moves.\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What I bring is creativity.\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2157, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All of my moves are original,\\\" she explained.\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Creativity is really important to me.\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I go out there, and I show my artistry.\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes it speaks to the judges, and sometimes it does not.\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do my thing, and it represents art.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That is what it is about.\\\"\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2409, \"entities\": []}]}"